3 SECTION 4. Part II of Act 250, Session Laws of
4 Hawaii 2025, is amended by amending section 3 to read as
5 follows:
6 "SECTION 3. APPROPRIATIONS. The following sums, or so
7 much thereof as may be sufficient to accomplish the purposes and
8 programs designated herein, are hereby appropriated or
9 authorized, as the case may be, from the means of financing
10 specified to the expending agencies designated for the fiscal
11 biennium beginning July 1, 2025, and ending June 30, 2027. The
12 total expenditures and the number of positions in each fiscal
13 year of the biennium shall not exceed the sums and the position
14 ceiling indicated for each fiscal year, except as provided
15 elsewhere in this Act, or as provided by general law.
